data.description: **BRAND NEW CARPET INSTALLED 10/15**  Spacious is how I would define this beautifully maintained 4 bedroom 3.5 bath home in Alamo Ranch. From the moment you step foot into the two story foyer, you'll be taken by the high ceilings, multiple living areas , a gigantic game room and a separate loft area perfect for a small study space. With the owner's suite located on the first floor, the home is set up for a variety of needs!
